title: Planet X - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 11/18/19

description:
George Noory and theoretical theologian Doug Elwell explore his research into the mysterious Planet X, which is rumored to return to our solar system every 3600 years, and whether disasters in the Bible might have been caused by the planet or fallen angels.
